title: Sailor Moon .m4v
description:
I was in the process of watching Sailor Moon, but wanted to be able to do it on my phone when I was bored but not at my computer... so I converted all the files to .m4v (iTunes compatible). I'm sure there will be few people interested, but I thought I would share it with those that would like the same capability. Quality is moderate; not great, but good enough to watch without issues (that I noticed anyway). 

Conversions were made using Handbrake, handbrake.fr.
